{"tid":1824700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【\t太監教行房\t】中國網友不滿小英當選 籲「14億人都來投票」被封帳","createTime":"2020-01-14T15:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T16:02:03.000Z","uid":236171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"587d7bff6a4ab768bf78752aa949fbf7dde73099","tid":1824700,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中國網友不滿小英當選 <br />\n籲「14億人都來投票」被封帳</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n總統蔡英文11日以817萬231票，擊潰國民黨總統落選人韓國瑜的552萬2119票，成功當選我國第15任總統，有中國網友對此表示不服，認為14億人都該投票決定，語畢就被中國網管封鎖帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">微博用戶「朴先生日記」發布貼文指出</span></strong>，<br />\n<br />\n「蔡英文連任台灣地區領導人（總統）的消息傳出之後，群裡一個粉紅憤憤不平地說：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">『台灣只有兩千多萬人，應該全中國14億人都來投票。』然後，他微信就被封號了。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但該則貼文疑似也違反中國法律，目前已被下架。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港臉書網友將這篇貼文截圖後發出，引發全球華人譏笑，不少人留言諷刺「中國人有票嗎？」、「蝗國人見過選票嗎？」、「怎麼不是14億人選習近平？」、「真是忍不住笑」、「仆街老共連投票也不能討論」、「蝗蟲太搞笑了」、「投個毛」、「弱智，五毛不只無腦這麼簡單」。"},{"pid":"90915bc22ff3d7181b9665a0401a6fb85fe2ec26","tid":1824700,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/3039135?utm_medium=P&amp;__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3039135%3Futm_medium%3DP%26__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=685281e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3039135%3Futm_medium%3DP%26__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&h=8b0f20a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/3039135?utm_medium=P&amp;__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"e119b0de907e4dcdc5cd5c524f9aead7e336a728","tid":1824700,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf13e41cf7df1e4abc807fdff028960a7c21f352","tid":1824700,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"禮拜五講座，手足們唔該幫推置頂<br />\n<br />\n【行動post】【吳敏兒和你組工會】1月17日（五）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7041da4a98a32776b0ed5b8af05c74fd669bba3","tid":1824700,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f29d6813f7ec25846f4b4a22b7f172f78bfaeb3","tid":1824700,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}